GlobalConst
public class LSHFLeafPage extends LSHFSortedPage
LSHFLeafPage is a leaf page in the LSH-Forest prefix tree. It stores <key, RID> pairs where the key is the hash value (a binary string) computed from a 100D vector. Overflow pages are handled via BTSortedPage.
